around with a short recovery in between

00:02:13.259 --> 00:02:16.199
or maybe minutes and a half to three
minutes in between each

00:02:16.199 --> 00:02:19.480
you get the neuromuscular benefit
of running at your race pace

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:24.510
and that makes the Tempo run much more
sensible. Also be you know be cautious

00:02:24.510 --> 00:02:28.180
with how many Tempo runs you do. you
